11 ther administer and pay the supplemental benefits directly or shall assign responsibility to
12 administer and process the payment to a paying agent selected by the director.
13 (6) The director shall adopt rules for the payment and reimbursement of supplemental temporary
14 disability benefits under this section.
15 SECTION 2. The amendments to ORS 656.210 by section 1 of this 2026 Act apply to claims
16 for temporary total disability compensation for injuries sustained or diseases incurred on or
17 after January 1, 2027.
